Description:
You come across a large airship. As you approach, a strange squid-headed humanoid with black eyes emerges from the deck and says to you:

"Come aboard travellers, I am Tsnemo, captain of this merchant ship. We sail the void between worlds in search of exotic relics and lost knowledge.

We are currently waiting for a delivery and are short of items.
DescriptionAction: But for some gold we can give you information about these ruins."
